data.description: Seller is offering $10,000 towards a rate buy down/Closing Costs. Come Home for the Holidays! Welcome to this beautiful 2 bedroom ~ 2 full bathroom lower level condo, perfectly situated in Beautiful Waterfront Benicia! This corner unit boasts of wonderful updates and is filled with natural light. Features include updated gorgeous kitchen, in unit laundry, living room with fireplace, sliding door from the living room that leads to the private deck. The gorgeous kitchen has been meticulously renovated to include sleek appliances including a wine fridge. Proximity to shopping, schools, freeways to Marin, Berkeley, Napa or San Francisco. Great Commute Location, Fabulous Opportunity to live in or have an Investment Property in the heart of Benicia!
